description: If you ♥️ this place as much as we do, make sure to leave a kind review over on Yelp and Facebook! I also saved my favorite Franklin places to my highlights. Janny and I have been eating here almost daily the last few weeks. My fav is the Caesar Wrap (those grilled lemons 🤤) and my drink of choice is a lavender latte (half sweet) with oat milk. So many organic and locally sourced ingredients with a curated menu that meets the needs of everyone! And hello, this Sunday they have a sweet menu for Father’s Day! #notanAD #justlove #franklintn #locallyowned #smallbusiness
